  - m_Id: 1057393978200088
    m_Localized: After The August Revolution's victory, the Vietnam's goverment has
      regained authorities from Japan
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200089
    m_Localized: Vietnam's President Ho Chi Minh read the declaration of independence
      at Ba Dinh square, Hanoi
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200090
    m_Localized: The Democratic Republic Of Vietnam
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200091
    m_Localized: However, Vietnam still had a lot of unsolved problem, Ho Chi Minh
      has pointed out three major of them
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200092
    m_Localized: First, illiteracy, the French Colonizer has initiated their Policy
      Of Ignorance which served them better to rule Vietnam
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200093
    m_Localized: Second, Starvation, the Imperial Japan has force farmers to get
      rid of wheats in order to planting Jute, leading to food supply shortage causing
      over 2 million citizens of Northern Vietnam starved to death
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200094
    m_Localized: And lastly, Foreign Invaders, France has clearly shown their intention
      of re-invading Vietnam once again
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200095
    m_Localized: But not just them, 20 million troops of Chiang Kai Shek marching
      toward Northern Vietnam, the UK under the Postdam Agreement has entered Southern
      Vietnam with fellow France among them
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200096
    m_Localized: 'The Vietnam want no war, so they has constantly negotiating for
      peace '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200097
    m_Localized: But the more they appease, the more aggressive France become
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200098
    m_Localized: In such situation, at night 19/12/1946, Ho Chi Minh has issued his
      speech to all Vietnamese citizens, Calls To The National Resistance
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200099
    m_Localized: The morality of fellow citizens to protect their homeland has been
      risen
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200100
    m_Localized: French Colonizer, after many times their ultimatum has been rejected,
      they begin to launch an attack on Hanoi
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200101
    m_Localized: 'In order to buy more time for Vietnam forces to moving to the Viet
      Bac Base, a lot of volunteers which formed the Capital Regiment decided to
      stay, using all they have to stop the French army '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200102
    m_Localized: This battle is just the beginning of the Indochina War, 60 days
      of flame and blood, many young soldiers has sacrified themselves that day for
      the nation to live
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200103
    m_Localized: Thanks to their bravery and sacrificion of the Capital Regiment's
      soldiers, the Vietnam forces has more time to completely moved to the Viet
      Bac Base, establishing long-term resistance
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200104
    m_Localized: Fall Winter Viet Bac Operation, also known ass Operation Lea, the
      French has set their objective to captured the Vietnam Force dead or alive,
      to put an end to the resistance of Vietnam
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200105
    m_Localized: In 07/10/1947, 800 French soldiers under the command of Colonel
      Henri Sauvanag set their foot on Bac Kan, attack many infrastructure such as
      hospital, factory
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200106
    m_Localized: In 08/10/1947 200 French parachute trooper attack Cho Don, the other
      forces under the command of Lieutenant colonel  Pierre Communal from Da & Gam
      river advanced to Phu Doan in 12, Tuyen Quang in 13 and Chiem Hoa in 17
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200107
    m_Localized: From another direction, 8000 foot soldiers by colonel Andre Beaufre
      commanded, from Lang Son along the colonal road 4 through Dong Nang, Na Cham,
      That Ke, Dong Khe to Cao Bang in 12/10/1947, then advanced to Bac Kan to surround
      Viet Bac Base from the East
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200108
    m_Localized: The airplane which was carrying 12 French Officers are on their
      way to observing the battlefield was shot down, the Vietnamese Force has taken
      their plan on Viet Bac Base Advancing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200109
    m_Localized: After retrieving the French's documents, the messenger solider Nguyen
      Danh Loc has went through the forest on his foot to deliver the document to
      the Headquarter
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200110
    m_Localized: After receiving the plan, Vietnam HQ has readjusted their forces
      for the counter attack
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200111
    m_Localized: At Song Lo - Road 2 field, Vietnamese troops under commands of Tran
      Tu Binh & Ta Xuan Thu, begin the counter attack on the French troops, cut their
      line of supply
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200112
    m_Localized: 'At Bac Kan - Road 3, Vietnamese troops with Hoang Van Thai commanded
      has the objective to eliminate the French troops '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200113
    m_Localized: At Road 4 field, Vo Nguyen Giap directly commanding the troop
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200114
    m_Localized: However, In France, their political state is in unstable condition,
      forced them has to end to battle with victory soon
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200115
    m_Localized: in 15/10, 2 Vietnam Battalion with one artillery team, advanced
      200 French soldier at Cho Moi
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200116
    m_Localized: in 22/10, Tuyen Quang self-defence forces used mine to ambush the
      French vehicles, eliminate 100 of them
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200117
    m_Localized: Also another 17 small ambushes on Phu Thong, Cho Moi - Bac Kan,
      causing fear in French soldiers, hesitating to moving further from their campsite
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200118
    m_Localized: No matter how strong an army is, one of the most vital point directly
      contributting to their combat strength is the logistic supply
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200119
    m_Localized: Due to that, The Vietnam HQ has issued to heavily strike at Lo river
      and Road 4 to cut their line of supply
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200120
    m_Localized: At Lo river, a group of 5 French boats from to Tuyen Quang on their
      way Doan Hung has been ambushed by artillery and RPG
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200121
    m_Localized: 2 has been sunken leading to all troop onboard drowned, other 2
      heavily disabled, the last one retreated back to Tuyen Quang
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200122
    m_Localized: Combining with "Empty houses, barren land" issued by the fellow
      civilians, cut their supply as well
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200123
    m_Localized: 'Due to this strategy, civilian has clean every food supply from
      their house, when the French troopers arrived, there is nothing left '
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200124
    m_Localized: After this battle, Lo river route has been cut for 10 days. French
      press called this event "Doan Hung Disaster"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200125
    m_Localized: From October to November, many ambushes and attack on the French
      causing them heavy casualties, their Lea Operation was a failed
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200126
    m_Localized: From 19/11 to 14/12/1947, The French still advancing at Tuyen Quang,
      Thai Nguyen, Phu Lang Thuong, Viet Tri
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393978200127
    m_Localized: French troops destroyed many infrastructure, captured many Vietnam
      civilians and rescued French prisoners
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393999171584
    m_Localized: French Goverment use this battle to consolidate their control over
      their colony, while the soldier keeping in mind that they are fighting for
      their country
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393999171585
    m_Localized: For some French soldier who is directly fought on the battlefield,
      some of them, doubting themselves for the war they are fighting, most of people
      die here are unarmed civilian
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393999171586
    m_Localized: Witnessing dead people, soldier, civilian corpses on the cold ground,
      they wonder, if those body down there was them someday
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393999171587
    m_Localized: On Viet Bac battlefield, many other battle occured, causing mass
      casualties, on Vietnam side, more and more civilian has died
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393999171588
    m_Localized: More conflict happen, even inside the city, Vietnam guerilla continously
      ambushed at Chem, Cau Giay, Van Dien, Vinh Tuy. Other happened not just in
      the Northern but also in the Southern
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1057393999171589
    m_Localized: French Commanders after realizing the table has been turned, they
      decided to retreat out of Viet Bac, from 06/12 to 19/12/1947, French Forces
      constantly got pushed back and ambushed on their way of retreating
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1741829455564800
    m_Localized: Press Any Button To Start
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12297507865710592
    m_Localized: Press Any Button To Continue
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12298813149892608
    m_Localized: Enemy plane, far, adjusting long range !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12299373357912064
    m_Localized: Enemy plane, incoming !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12299652077801472
    m_Localized: They are getting closer ! Keep firing !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12299781555965952
    m_Localized: They are on our head !!!!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12299899390742528
    m_Localized: Too far ! That won't take them down ! Readjust !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12300031582621696
    m_Localized: We need to bring the shell closer !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12300441932353536
    m_Localized: Almost there ! Adjust a little bit and keep firing !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12300646652137472
    m_Localized: Those motherfucker is burning ! Keep firing !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 12300758015102976
    m_Localized: Bite the dust motherfucker !
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13334069944602624
    m_Localized: Play Demo
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 13336607221698560
    m_Localized: 'This demo version was built specifically for Graduation Project


      Further
      campaign of this project will be released in the future'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 14350052155019264
    m_Localized: 'GIANG MO VILLAGE

      13/12/1951'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15145634146635776
    m_Localized: 'WARNING INDICATOR


      This warning sigh appearance notify player
      where the mortar shell will hit, stay away from it'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15139831633235968
    m_Localized: 'This game is a work of fiction inspired by real historical events.
      While certain locations, events, and figures are based on actual history, the
      story, characters, and specific scenarios depicted in this game have been fictionalized
      for the purposes of narrative and gameplay.


      The game does not intend
      to represent any real person, organization, or belief system with complete
      accuracy. Any similarities to real people, living or deceased, are purely coincidental
      unless otherwise stated.


      This work is meant to honor the memory of
      those affected by the events portrayed and is not intended to diminish or distort
      the historical significance of those events. We encourage players to explore
      verified historical sources for a deeper understanding.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 15860888317022208
    m_Localized: 'This function is still in development

      Stay Tuned !'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21413792167841792
    m_Localized: This is our demo for our game, thanks for playing
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
